  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t成年排名#1的王楚钦已经被淘汰了。四强里的<mark>支那人</mark>只剩下樊振东。<br/>\n<br/>\n法国小将，世界青少排名#1的Félix Lebrun 发推了：<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS95NFl6V0FZLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/y4YzWAY.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/y4YzWAY.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/y4YzWAY.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9haVJsVDh2LmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/aiRlT8v.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/aiRlT8v.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aiRlT8v.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>Félix Lebrun，2006年生人，17岁，目前在世界青少排第一！</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9QTkxpV05jLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/PNLiWNc.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/PNLiWNc.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PNLiWNc.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>樊振东，27岁，目前成人排第四。</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9zT3JSbWs4LnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/sOrRmk8.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/sOrRmk8.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sOrRmk8.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n排第一的王楚钦已经被淘汰了。如果 Félix Lebrun 能打败樊振东，那今年<mark>支那</mark>男单最多只能拿个铜。<mark>支那</mark>要是丢了乒乓球金牌，那场面一定。。。。。。美！<br/>\n<br/>\n<b>8/2 北京时间下午5点，美东时间上午5点，有葱友打算看吗？</b> </div>",
